data.description: Excellent House located in Gated Community with a pond just off the back deck. Many upgrades including Gas Stove, Water Heater, high impact garage door and a new fence all in 2023. There are also many upgrades since the purchase including a new fridge, storm door, driveway extended, deck extended, barn door on the bathroom and 6 inch gutters all the way around. Lawn care and garbage pick-up is included in the HOA. Don't miss your chance to view this fabulous house in PCB.
